Rakes are used in the Farming skill to remove weeds from farming patches. It can be bought from Farming shops. In addition, it can also be purchased from most of the gardeners who look after your farming patches. A tool leprechaun can store one for you.

In addition, it can also be purchased from most of the [[Group of Advanced Gardeners|gardeners]] who look after your farming patches. A [[tool leprechaun]] can store one for you.
